name: Egg Animals (conclusion)
description: On the 13th day, the dark power shrouded the whole forest. Animals have no power to fight these evil unknown creatures. To protect their homes. The animals gathered together. Use the last strength to try to summon the ancient patron saint of the forest - Dragon. With a flash of lightning. A dragon broke its egg.Using the bravery and tenacity of animals, seven dragon balls were made. Lit up the whole forest. So far, the dark forces were completely expelled from the forest. The story of the egg animal is over. From then on, there will be no dark creatures in the forest. There will be no new egg animals. (as for the story of dark creatures, I think they will have their own independent story. Please look forward to...)
